### contain: layout;
```css
.parent-div {
  contain: layout;
}
```

### contain: paint;
```css
.parent-div {
  contain: paint;
}
```

### contain: size
```css
.parent-div {
  contain: size;
}
```

### contain: style;
```css
.parent-div {
  contain: style;
}
```

If you find any mistake in the above explanation or demo, feel free to [raise an issue](https://github.com/termvader/css-contain/issues/new) or [fork & suggest changes](https://github.com/termvader/css-contain)
